<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>국외 결제 확인</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-50 to-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-8">
        <div class="w-full max-w-md bg-white/90 backdrop-blur rounded-xl shadow-lg ring-1 ring-slate-200 p-6 md:p-8">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">국외 결제 확인</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">아래 결제를 승인하시겠습니까?</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 divide-y divide-slate-200">
                <div class="py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">가맹점</span>
                    <span class="text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-slate-800">{{storeName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">국가</span>
                    <span class="text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-slate-800">{{country}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">금액</span>
                    <span class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-blue-700">{{amount}}원</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <button
                    class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 active:bg-blue-800 shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-white transition"
                    onclick="location.href='/verify/{{transactionId}}/approve'"
                >
                    승인
                </button>
                <button
                    class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-slate-800 bg-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-400 active:bg-slate-500 shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-300 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-white transition"
                    onclick="location.href='/verify/{{transactionId}}/deny'"
                >
                    거절
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>